{"tid":2445584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指違反防疫規定  俄國警方中斷反對派會議　拘捕約200人","createTime":"2021-03-13T17:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T01:06:26.000Z","uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4a203f6fb90ff7032a00308e5aeee023010d9e62","tid":2445584,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:31:10.000Z","msg":"俄國警方中斷反對派會議　拘捕約200人<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯警方中斷一個反對派會議，拘捕大約200人，包括著名的反對派人物。有關論壇周末起，一連兩日在首都莫斯科一間酒店舉行，來自全國各地的反對派人士，討論9月的地方及議會選舉策略。警方星期六突然衝入會場，表示現場很多人違反防疫規定，論壇亦是由一個不良組織發起，所有人都被捕。電視片段顯示，參加者被帶上警車。協助組織論壇的反對派人士批評，當局是要阻嚇民眾；反對派領袖納瓦爾尼的盟友說，當局明顯很怕在選舉中有競爭對手。<br />\n<br />\n2021-03-14 01:10:34<br />\nhttps://new<del><a href=\"http://s.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580449-202103\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580449-202103&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=9e342461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">s.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580449-202103</a></del>14.htm"},{"pid":"a4efc715f58be9acf1df8d14e9a2030f49942f78","tid":2445584,"uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:34:22.000Z","msg":"俄版599G<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ac7f95632bceed7bc43b633ad65f93b8841b02","tid":2445584,"uid":3860,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:36:56.000Z","msg":"世界極權政府都靠防疫打壓反對聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b7885c50b57bf1e2f5c16cb3e0be7648993251","tid":2445584,"uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:37:00.000Z","msg":"香港都走得好前<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22bd2f13db9768e4ba649264e5aebd49978c6aa","tid":2445584,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c7db5c2103f0e2a563b094ad8d383a6b0